Frontend: React (17+), Tailwind CSS, React Router, PWA support for offline.

Backend: Node.js (16+), Express.js, RESTful APIs.

Database: PostgreSQL on AWS RDS.

AI Integration: OpenAI GPT-4 via secure server-side proxies.

Maps: Mapbox GL JS (or Google Maps JS SDK), Mapbox Directions API.

Auth: OAuth2 with Google, Apple; SMS OTP via AWS SNS.

Hosting/Infra: AWS ECS (Docker), AWS Fargate, AWS S3 (static assets), AWS CloudFront, AWS SNS (push notifications).

CI/CD: CircleCI pipelines (build, test, deploy to staging/prod).

Testing: Jest for unit tests, Supertest for API tests.